      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EXTRAVAGANTLY (4) had the drop on the lead before drawing clear to score (23.60) at this track in a TG1-4W over 400m. Can make it two on the bounce. LADY ROSALYN (7) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 4 lengths at this track in a handy 23.63 beating Costly Habits. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Deserves serious consideration again. PATTY'S DREAM (1) has mixed form recently, finishing eighth (27.12) in a Bottom Up - Grade 5 at Warrnambool latest but did run well two back when in the frame. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. MISTY AUTUMN (2) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to make amends.",
